patthana19.5:1.1: Nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca asaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. patthana19.5:4.1: Hetuyā aṭṭhārasa, ārammaṇe nava …pe… vipāke ekādasa …pe… avigate aṭṭhārasa.
